  "Communities should not advocate for environmental cleanup": "",
  "The NIMBY phenomenon was successfully overcome": "",
  "This cycle reveals that environmental remediation without protections against displacement (like affordable housing requirements) can lead to environmental gentrification, where the communities that fought for cleanup are pushed into new environmental hazard zones.": "",
